# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq0.rpy:14
translate chinese mariq0_7430c95e:

    # fr "So, do you live by yourself?"
    fr "那么，你一个人住吗？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq0.rpy:15
translate chinese mariq0_435d3697:

    # pc "No. Right now I live with my [mother] and [sister] in the house that I grew up in."
    pc "不。我现在和我的[mother]、[sister]住在我长大的那栋房子里。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq0.rpy:16
translate chinese mariq0_87f506ec:

    # pc "It's my dad's house, but he's not there right now."
    pc "那是爸爸的房子，但他现在不在那里。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq0.rpy:17
translate chinese mariq0_95def8b6:

    # fr "Oh? Where is he?"
    fr "哦？他在哪里？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq0.rpy:18
translate chinese mariq0_34d4f370:

    # pc "That's the thing. We don't know."
    pc "问题就在这里。我们不知道。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq0.rpy:19
translate chinese mariq0_05820813:

    # pc "That's why I came home - to help find him."
    pc "这就是我回家的原因——帮忙找他。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq0.rpy:20
translate chinese mariq0_8dee027a:

    # pc "He just disappeared and we don't have a lot of clues."
    pc "他突然失踪了，我们手头线索很少。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq0.rpy:23
translate chinese mariq0_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/mari_aww2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_aww2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq0.rpy:24
translate chinese mariq0_001d05e3:

    # fr "Aww... I'm so sorry."
    fr "哎呀……。真抱歉。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq0.rpy:25
translate chinese mariq0_fc7f31c9:

    # pc "It's okay. I think that we'll find him eventually."
    pc "没关系。我相信我们终会找到他的。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq0.rpy:26
translate chinese mariq0_3849e3ab:

    # pc "I've been talking with the police and we're keeping our hopes up."
    pc "我一直在和警方沟通，我们一直抱有希望。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq0.rpy:27
translate chinese mariq0_8aeb9a7f:

    # fr "That's good. I really hope you do."
    fr "那太好了。我真心希望你们能找到他。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq0.rpy:28
translate chinese mariq0_49c46e93:

    # fr "I know what it's like to lose family. It's horrible."
    fr "我深知失去亲人的滋味。那感觉太可怕了。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq0.rpy:29
translate chinese mariq0_d153400b:

    # fr "I would never wish it on anyone. Especially you."
    fr "我绝不会希望任何人经历这种事。尤其是你。"

